00:44:41.130 --> 00:44:42.820
to mine data.

00:44:42.820 --> 00:44:44.610
Where do you think
it's heading now?

00:44:44.610 --> 00:44:46.620
And what steps should
we take to make

00:44:46.620 --> 00:44:49.540
it more meaningful to society?

00:44:49.540 --> 00:44:51.570
NOAM CHOMSKY: Well, I
