But it's a distortion
of the world in ways

00:54:15.490 --> 00:54:17.630
that shouldn't be happening.

00:54:17.630 --> 00:54:20.680
So the actual news, I
think, should be what

00:54:20.680 --> 00:54:22.690
we've just been talking about.

00:54:22.690 --> 00:54:24.520
Like why are we--

00:54:24.520 --> 00:54:27.430
why for the last
generation have we

00:54:27.430 --> 00:54:32.260
constructed socioeconomic
policies and political policies

00:54:32.260 --> 00:54:37.070
which are developing a perfect
storm which could destroy us.

00:54:37.070 --> 00:54:39.610
SPEAKER 1: So if we
can devise a way for--

00:54:39.610 --> 00:54:42.520
I mean obviously advertising
monetization is the way

00:54:42.520 --> 00:54:45.490
