00:55:39.460 --> 00:55:42.760
the most popular
widely read newspaper

00:55:42.760 --> 00:55:47.650
was "The Daily Herald," which
was kind of social-democratic.

00:55:47.650 --> 00:55:51.010
The tabloids in England,
which are now monstrous,

00:55:51.010 --> 00:55:54.490
were labor based newspapers
and pretty interesting.

00:55:54.490 --> 00:55:57.850
They succumbed to
the consequences

00:55:57.850 --> 00:56:01.750
of capital concentration,
and advertiser reliance,

00:56:01.750 --> 00:56:03.850
and became quite different.

00:56:03.850 --> 00:56:06.370
Similar here.

00:56:06.370 --> 00:56:07.930
When I was a kid
growing up, there

00:56:07.930 --> 00:56:11.500
were several newspapers
delivered, local newspapers,

00:56:11.500 --> 00:56:13.330
delivered every day.

00:56:13.330 --> 00:56:16.520
They were not-- there
was a certain variety.

00:56:16.520 --> 00:56:20.290
Now in Boston, now
there isn't even one.

00:56:20.290 --> 00:56:25.860
"The Boston Globe" used to
be a pretty decent newspaper,

00:56:25.860 --> 00:56:28.270
problems, but a
lot of bureaus all

00:56:28.270 --> 00:56:30.940
over the world, good reporters.

00:56:30.940 --> 00:56:33.415
Take a look at it now.

00:56:33.415 --> 00:56:35.740
It basically doesn't exist.

00:56:35.740 --> 00:56:37.660
It has some local news.

00:56:37.660 --> 00:56:40.480
And the rest, it picks
up "The New York Times,"

00:56:40.480 --> 00:56:43.630
"Washington Post," the AP.

00:56:43.630 --> 00:56:46.450
That's happened all
over the country.

00:56:46.450 --> 00:56:49.300
It has a lot of
reasons behind it.

00:56:49.300 --> 00:56:52.570
But the large part of
it-- it's been going on

00:56:52.570 --> 00:56:53.560
for over a century.

00:56:53.560 --> 00:56:54.960
It's just continuing.

00:56:54.960 --> 00:56:58.470
The large part is the effect
of capital concentration

00:56:58.470 --> 00:56:59.920
and advertiser reliance.

00:56:59.920 --> 00:57:04.012
Which affects the content of
the media reporting as well.

00:57:04.012 --> 00:57:06.220
SPEAKER 1: In that case,
we'll cancel our advertising

00:57:06.220 --> 00:57:06.934
