00:57:10.600 --> 00:57:13.060
Any of you that have
taken an economics course

00:57:13.060 --> 00:57:18.040
know that the
beauty, the marvels

00:57:18.040 --> 00:57:21.810
of the market that we're
supposed to admire and worship

00:57:21.810 --> 00:57:27.770
is because the market is based
on informed consumers making

00:57:27.770 --> 00:57:29.090
rational choices.

00:57:29.090 --> 00:57:32.180
And you prove all sorts of
theorems about how wonderful

00:57:32.180 --> 00:57:34.150
it is.

00:57:34.150 --> 00:57:37.310
Turn on your television set.

00:57:37.310 --> 00:57:40.670
Do you see efforts
by corporations

00:57:40.670 --> 00:57:46.790
to create informed consumers
making rational choices?

00:57:46.790 --> 00:57:50.260
Is that what you see when
you see an ad for cars?

00:57:50.260 --> 00:57:52.760
I mean, if we had a
market system, what

00:57:52.760 --> 00:57:58.100
you would see is when General
Motors is advertising a car,

00:57:58.100 --> 00:58:03.350
what you would see is a list of
the characteristics of the car,

00:58:03.350 --> 00:58:06.170
along with a report
by "Consumers Report"

00:58:06.170 --> 00:58:08.900
saying what's wrong
with it and so on.

00:58:08.900 --> 00:58:11.060
That would create
informed consumers that

00:58:11.060 --> 00:58:12.560
could make rational choices.

00:58:12.560 --> 00:58:14.360
But you don't see that.

00:58:14.360 --> 00:58:17.040
What you see is an
effort to delude,

00:58:17.040 --> 00:58:20.970
you know, a movie star,
a football player,

00:58:20.970 --> 00:58:23.690
a car shooting up
into the stratosphere,

00:58:23.690 --> 00:58:25.760
wherever it may be.

00:58:25.760 --> 00:58:30.380
Huge amounts of capital
are expended every year

00:58:30.380 --> 00:58:34.100
to try to undermine
markets, undermine markets

00:58:34.100 --> 00:58:39.110
by creating uninformed consumers
making irrational choices,

00:58:39.110 --> 00:58:43.340
and driving them to
consumerism, which atomizes

00:58:43.340 --> 00:58:45.560
rather than serious things.

00:58:45.560 --> 00:58:49.250
